OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with patchy rain. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be cloudy
OL,8,Fwith rain spreading to the west coast,
OL,9,Fbut dry elsewhere.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FCloudy with rain across the
OL,12,Fwest in the morning, this spreading
OL,13,Facross eastern parts in the afternoon.
OL,14,FTurning drier across the west through
OL,15,Fthe afternoon. Mild around Inverness
OL,16,Fand Nairn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
