OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny spells on Friday
OL,7,Fand Saturday, becoming windy in the
OL,8,Ffar northwest. Cloudy on Sunday with
OL,9,Foccasional rain.
